hackathon-description-text: HackNotts is a 24 hour Hackathon hosted at the University of Nottingham. In October this year we will be returning for our fourth year! Join us for a weekend of hacking and fun in the stunning Jubilee Campus.
hackathon-eligibility: All students that have bought a ticket :)
hackathon-rules: See the MLH Code of Conduct
